{
  "title": "Delicate Silky Egyptian Bacon Pilaf",
  "description": "A malty, silky, and comforting Egyptian dish featuring streaky bacon, this pilaf is a raw-friendly and blanch-friendly meal option. It combines the richness of bacon with the simplicity of Egyptian spices.",
  "cuisine": "Egyptian",
  "diet": [
